              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "REAC"
                ],
                "institute": "4ZZZDUB"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "  Reactor IBR-2.",
                " Spectrometric setup consist of two rotor-type",
                " mechanical neutron choppers with dc motors,",
                " an electronic system for stabilizing the rotation of",
                " rotors and phasing the moment of opening slits along",
                " a neutron beam with a neutron pulse,collimators, and",
                " neutron detectors.",
                " The angular rotational velocity of rotors changes from",
                " 0 to 6000 rpm, their synchronization with the neutron",
                " pulse is provided with accuracy of 10 microsec  at",
                " minimum time of opening slits along the neutron beam",
                " of 20 microsec."
              ]
            }
          ],
